                    PROBE CyberPaint Animation
                      by Kevin Steele  9/88

     A probe spins through the void of space, approaching and
landing on an alien world. This starflight sequence was created
using CyberPaint 2.0, a truly exceptional graphics program. As it
was created on a Mega ST2, I really can't guarantee that it will
run on a 1040, although I have tried to keep it short. I've
included the new ANIMATE4.PRG necessary for 2.0 animations, and
the accompanying documentation. If you have any comments about
this animation, feel free to drop me a note.

Kevin Steele
